                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Hold, resident. This quarry road is under a Company haulage contract. Foot traffic is unlicensed tonnage. You may pay tonnage, or you may become an obstruction, which we clear."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The stone here has a grade now. So does everyone who walks past it. Do not ask for yours."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Unlicensed tonnage on a Company road. Refuse the toll and we settle it the hard way, or step off the ledge and we forget you."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Contractor - the toll",
                    Label: "quarry_hail"
                },
